short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save and organize Chrome tabs by lists

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tabs Later helps you to organize loads of opened tabs to keep browser clean, and help productivity.

➤ View, search, and manage opened tabs.
➤ Select and save opened tabs into lists at will
➤ Manage list and its content.
➤ Import and export lists.
